Package com.pyszkowski.http

This package contains an implementation of a simple http server.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HttpResponse
    Represents a http response.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppServer
    The main class that starts the server from the command line.
    BaseHttpResponse
    Basic implementation of the http response.
    HttpRequest
    Represents a http request.
    HttpRequestHandler
    Handles a http communication over a socket in a separate thread.
    Server
    Implements a http server main loop.
    Server.HttpHandlerRegistration
    Contains fields to match a HttpRequest to an instance of HttpMethodHandler.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HttpHeader
    Contains a subset of frequently used http headers.
    HttpMethod
    Contains a subset of http request methods.
    HttpResponseStatus
    Contains most frequently used http response statuses.
